node.text: Happy Sunday, friends! I don’t know if anyone is shopping for fall clothes yet, but, if so, this post is for you.😁👆🏼 // Leggings are 30% OFF + free ship (ends today). Under $20 tees, a $20 maxi dress, under $25 jeans and an Amazon blazer I’m loving! *All items linked in my IG bio. #readyforcoolertemps #tiredofsweating #fallstyle

node.text: Found this pic in my phone from May that I never posted. Not sure why because I love it!👯‍♀️ // p.s Thanks for loving on Camden today and his freshly permed mullet!😁 Remi is up next for a trim tomorrow…but no perm!😆 So grateful for this community of kind, hilarious, and uplifting women! Y’all are my people!🙌🏼 // *outifts linked in my IG bio. #mygirl #twinning #mamabear #summertime #mulletmom

node.text: Twinning with my best girl!👯‍♀️ // I’ve been meaning to ask y’all what you’re doing for the holiday weekend.  Staying in town, going out of town, having a BBQ, a firework show, the lake…all of the above?😁 Would love to hear what y’all will be up to! // Outfits linked in my bio. Tees are from @pinklily. You can use Jen20 for 20% off their site. #twinning #mygirl #mommyandme

node.text:
Laugher, lobster rolls, and living proof.💃🏻 Boston did not disappoint! We definitely want to go back and take our husbands because there’s so much there that we still want to do…and eat! What’s a city that you love to visit and/or hope to visit soon? // *outfits linked in my IG bio.😘
#boston #shenanigans #besties #outfits

node.text: I’m really excited about this photo dump of outfits! So many great *affordable* finds! The most flattering $36 wrap dress with adjustable straps😍, $20 maxi skirt that would be great for July 4th, under $30 dresses that could be cute for summer weddings, under $20 kimonos great for date night, $5 tanks and more! Would love your feedback on this roundup and what you’re loving! *ALL items linked in my IG bio.💃🏻 Xo! #affordablestyle #outfitinspo
